00:37:10.960 --> 00:37:14.640
that they become one
of the last voices

00:37:14.640 --> 00:37:18.620
for Anglo-American
culture in occupied Europe.

00:37:18.620 --> 00:37:22.110
And it's my hope that through
the recovery of more documents

00:37:22.110 --> 00:37:24.880
over time, that we'll actually
build a better understanding

00:37:24.880 --> 00:37:27.500
of what these brightly bound
books meant to the readers

00:37:27.500 --> 00:37:31.750
who accessed them under the
occupation and under fascism.

